  "commit_message": "fix(ui): notifications inbox — tab badge unfiltered + loadInbox refreshes it\n\nLayer-2 review on slice-5 found that loadInbox() wrote inboxUnreadCount\nfrom page.unreadCount, which is the filtered count (matches the page's\nstatus / eventType / unreadOnly). The tab badge needs the org-wide\ntotal, otherwise a status=FAILED filter would silently shrink the badge\nto \"FAILED-only unread\" and an admin with 100 unread items would see a\n5 next to \"Inbox\".\n\nStop loadInbox from touching inboxUnreadCount and",
